/乌头碱\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E4%B9%8C%E5%A4%B4%E7%A2%B1&d=65zmiEDbFJOKx0AN6DD1dIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=30b906ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/乌头碱</a><br />\n<br />\n佢應該係講緊中藥的烏頭, 唔係魚果種"},{"pid":"ad7891ef878a67f74717d85511753529c7fff655","tid":654791,"uid":72730,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"quote":{"pid":"8b5e92e91544972233ffc7e1dc272a3de9817915","tid":654791,"uid":2889,"like":14,"dislike":112,"score":-98,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T02:53:34.000Z","msg":"烏頭有毒既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？魚黎喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T02:56:59.000Z","msg":"烏頭鹼（Aconitine）是常用中藥烏頭中所含有的一種化學物質，具強烈毒性，口服0.2mg左右即能使人中毒，3&mdash;5mg即可致死。民間常用草烏、川烏等植物來泡製藥酒。"},{"pid":"45bd7299d2146fa3fab3efc81030c59a5a0899c8","tid":654791,"uid":52946,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T02:57:46.000Z","msg":"佢朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce8d56c1a6da8dad9c39706d401b717c50c18bdb","tid":654791,"uid":10503,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T02:59:34.000Z","msg":"支那人真係特別on9"},{"pid":"50fb8271a009d9e1a5c56dbf88494ee8f37da0d0","tid":654791,"uid":62409,"like":359,"dislike":1,"score":358,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T03:00:30.000Z","msg":"在大陸的鄉下,一個老農夫，買來種子播下，到秋後竟然顆粒無收，因為種子是假的。老農決心一死，買來一瓶農藥喝下，結果沒死，因為農藥也是假的。由於人沒死，一家人慶幸，買來一瓶好酒全家喝，結果全家人都死了，因為酒也是假的。"},{"pid":"3c28fdd08114cfc2d10b527c8043b06fdd914b54","tid":654791,"uid":54927,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T03:01:47.000Z","msg":"咁撚中意飲酒 抵撚死"},{"pid":"1fc7741e7d53ecf316ac593e730fb4f244395faa","tid":654791,"uid":52946,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"50fb8271a009d9e1a5c56dbf88494ee8f37da0d0","tid":654791,"uid":62409,"like":359,"dislike":1,"score":358,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T03:00:30.000Z","msg":"在大陸的鄉下,一個老農夫，買來種子播下，到秋後竟然顆粒無收，因為種子是假的。老農決心一死，買來一瓶農藥喝下，結果