ike":41,"score":-41,"quote":{"pid":"1882a74d367b174a5b511068f792a9767da54ccc","tid":654791,"uid":174601,"like":152,"dislike":2,"score":150,"quote":{"pid":"8b5e92e91544972233ffc7e1dc272a3de9817915","tid":654791,"uid":2889,"like":14,"dislike":112,"score":-98,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T02:53:34.000Z","msg":"烏頭有毒既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？魚黎喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T02:54:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/乌头碱\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%E4%B9%8C%E5%A4%B4%E7%A2%B1&d=65zmiEDbFJOKx0AN6DD1dIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=3e2b791e\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/乌头碱</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我喜歡你的思路"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T06:02:06.000Z","msg":"我都以為系😅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T06:54:45.000Z","msg":"系你老母殘體狗<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Sky_Croc 事件撮要</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/06/001942_a79460cd1138de92ec127b087ddeaca6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F06%2F001942_a79460cd1138de92ec127b087ddeaca6.png&h=ea1111f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Sky_Croc真係高登最黑人憎嘅會員</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://hkgalden.com/view/103703\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkgalden.com%2Fview%2F103703&d=65zmiEDbFJOKx0AN6DD1dIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=c03ba189\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkgalden.com/view/103703</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>雖則唔會再上高登留言但見到呢件人間垃圾都認唔住想鬧佢呢個殘體人<br />\n<br />\n呢條友成日扮哂野咁係各個ＰＯＳＴ到留言 <br />\n每次留親都用標準既殘體字 <br />\n呢條仆街係咪收左錢要潛移默化香港人用殘體？ <br />\n<br />\n我知道唔人已經ＢＬＯＣＫ左佢 <br />\n但係我仲見到呢條仆街ＫＥＥＰ住留言我真係眼火爆<br />\n<br />\n例子：＃８ <br />\n<a href=\"https://web.hkgolden.com/view/4694636\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.hkgolden.com%2Fview%2F4694636&d=65zmiEDbFJOKx0AN6DD1dIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=a00f1dfc\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.hkgolden.com/view/4694636</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>你老味Sky_Croc冇撚野下話, 個標題係繁體, 但個內文</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://web.hkgolden.com/view/5024501\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.hkgolden.com%2Fview%2F5024501&d=65zmiEDbFJOKx0AN6DD1dIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=8ce5fa4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.hkgolden.com/view/5024501</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>屌你老味</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">個標題係繁體, 但個內文都要打簡體?</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[CH13] 原來16年前&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum9.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=5024283&amp;highlight_id=228121\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum9.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D5024283%26highlight_id%3D228121&d=65zmiEDbFJOKx0AN6DD1dIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=da9825d0\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum9.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=5024283&amp;highlight_id=228121</a><br />\n<br />\n[魚蛋論] 點解以前唔向中國移動執法???<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum9.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=5021328&amp;highlight_id=228121\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum9.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D5021328%26highlight_id%3D228121&d=65zmiEDbFJOKx0AN6DD1dIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=d59a2b12\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum9.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=5021328&amp;highlight_id=228121</a><br />\n<br />\n[龍門系列] 相對於 香港人 同 新香港人<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum9.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=5013720&amp;page=1&amp;highlight_id=228121\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum9.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D5013720%26page%3D1%26highlight_id%3D228121&d=65zmiEDbFJOKx0AN6DD1dIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=3815e2e8\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum9.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=5013720&amp;page=1&amp;highlight_id=228121</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n會員編號: 228121<br />\n膠名: Sky Croc<br />\n加入日期: 8/10/2009<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum9.hkgolden.com/ProfilePage.aspx?userid=228121\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum9.hkgolden.com%2FProfilePage.aspx%3Fuserid%3D228121&d=65zmiEDbFJOKx0AN6DD1dIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=973b3c92\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum9.hkgolden.com/ProfilePage.aspx?userid=228121</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>佢幾年前就開始特登打簡體<br />\n<br />\n睇佢D語氣同用字同香港人一樣<br />\n<br />\n我諗佢係特登咁做，引人屌柒佢<br />\n<br />\n我諗佢係用心良苦，時時刻刻等人屌柒簡體<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係既話我屌佢全家</blockquote>"},{"pid":"87dad80f563bc0f7bf861ceaf1c2e21a035005d0","tid":654791,"uid":32706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T06:56:22.000Z","msg":"生日變死忌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a92f902a486de9957a35ca4a53f9ecd77c60823","tid":654791,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T06:58:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7593a87b93a7269c790b8d60634008ad2eaaa66","tid":654791,"uid":46493,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"3fb47a0beef86ba6679683c722a84adcae9c1a53","tid":654791,"uid":49004,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T03:18:40.000Z","msg":"在大陸的鄉下,一個老農夫，買來種子播下，到秋後竟然顆粒無收，因為種子是假的。老農決心一死，買來一瓶農藥喝下，結果沒死，因為農藥也是假的。由於人沒死，一家人慶幸，買來一瓶好酒全家喝，結果全家人都死了，因為酒也是假的。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T06:59:02.000Z","msg":"然後讀者求證事發地，發現這篇新聞也是假的"},{"pid":"28e059539b18bdefa05822adaa1fb6661a26a7f4","tid":654791,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T07:01:27.000Z","msg":"又唔問清楚個朋友係外敷定內服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif